<refsection condition='ref.description'>
<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>Procedure</tag> describes a sequence of
<tag>Step</tag>s that a reader is expected to perform.  If a
finer level of granularity is required for some steps, you can
use <tag>SubSteps</tag> to embed substeps within a
<tag>Step</tag>.
</para>
<para><tag>SubSteps</tag> contain <tag>Step</tag>s, so substeps can
be nested to any depth.
</para>

<refsection><title>Processing expectations</title>
<para><?tdg gentext='format.block'?>
<tag>SubStep</tag>s are almost always numbered.
</para>
